Package game

Enum Status

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Status>
game.Status
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Status>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Status
extends java.lang.Enum<Status>
Use this enum class to give `buff` or `debuff`. It is also useful to give a `state` to abilities or actions that can be attached-detached.
